Text: i am completely in the dark about this, so: what is terragen 2 deep edition?

@D34THW41K3R, do you mean what is the Deep Edition of Terragen?  It's just their name for the paid, commercially licensed version, without all the rendering limitations of the free version.  There are only 2 editions of Terragen; Free and "Deep".
